        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Calculated from production volume of reference product using the relative outputs. On average between 20214 and 2018, in France + Belgium + Netherlands 73 000 tons of flax, fibre, short scutched were produced per year. Source: statistic data for production of retted straw and of long and short fibres. The data was gathered by the Flax-Linen Economic Observatory of the Alliance for Linen-Flax and Hemp, from national organisations for flax cultivation and scutching in France, Belgium and the Netherlands.</productionVolumeComment>
